RN6.6.0-MU5: Adds resolved issues to the MU section

Adds fixed bugs for:

- Horizon (1468744): Sanitation of metadata label (CVE-2015-3988);
- Glance (1463522): Glance creating heavy CPU load on standby cluster;
- Swift (1466101): upstart mechanism is broken on controllers;
- Heat (1481197): Resource group with a nested wait condition handle
  fails on create,
- Neutron (1429065): neutron security-group-rule-list returnes
  "RequestURITooLong";
- Cinder (1459781): [CINDER][CEPH]cinder-volume can't be deleted during
  rally test.

- Fuel known issue (1465771): text amendment

